### Test Prisma Connection
GET {{baseUrl}}/test

### Chat with AI
POST {{baseUrl}}/chatbot/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "I have some leftover chicken and rice. What can I make?",
    "userId": "{{userId}}"
}

### Chat with AI (Continue Session)
# Replace sessionId with one returned from the previous request
POST {{baseUrl}}/chatbot/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Can you make it spicy?",
    "userId": "{{userId}}",
    "sessionId": "cm3t5v8u00000v8u0v8u0v8u1"
