### Get Chat History
GET {{baseUrl}}/chatbot/history?userId={{userId}}&limit=5

### Delete Chat Session
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/chatbot/history
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sessionId": "cm3t5v8u00000v8u0v8u0v8u1",
    "userId": "{{userId}}"
}

